commit_list.message:
Adding nest element to keep site from expanding indefinitely.

A non-semantic HTML element of div.nest auto-margins the elements so they appear to center once the main window of the browser is larger than 960px. It's not pretty, but it works. And we can set the sizing dependent upon the media queries as well, etc.
